    "services.automation.page.titleAccent": "Automation",
    "services.automation.page.description": "Industrial automation and IIoT for manufacturing and physical operations. System integration, PLC programming, HMI/SCADA development, robotics integration, predictive maintenance, and production monitoring. We build the control layer and the modern data and edge layer on top of it, so sensors and machines get connected, monitored, and made smarter by one team.",
